  ('medical-tech-moex-10802', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-104-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '在變性梯度膠體電泳法（Denaturing gradient gel electrophoresis, DGGE）中，通常要在其 中一條PCR引子的 5'' 端接上何種結構的分子，以避免在高濃度的變性劑存在下，所有的 DNA皆變成單股？', '["GC clamp", "AT clamp", "Poly-A", "5'' cap"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "51c839d0cd7d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9e674626cf68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104090", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第二次專技醫師牙醫師藥師分階段考試藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-10803', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-104-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於微陣列晶片（Microarray chip），下列敘述何者正確？', '["蛋白質晶片只適合用來偵測檢體中的蛋白質", "固定在DNA晶片上的DNA探針本身並未標示螢光物質或放射線同位素", "醣類晶片和蛋白質晶片均是以三度空間的特異構型為辨識結合基礎，但醣類的特異構型較 不穩定", "醣類晶片主要應用在偵測細胞內醣類的變化"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "51c839d0cd7d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9e674626cf68", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104090", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第二次專技醫師牙醫師藥師分階段考試藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 51, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
